author: perryan
msg: test.xml updated to use the specified endpoint if it is present in the test.endpoints properties file, otherwise it will use the default test endpoint. If the endpoint specified in the test.endpoints file is the string useSpecifiedServerPort, then the string -p ${testPort} -s ${testHost} will be passed to the client, with the values having been substituted of course.
